Fontes

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Kdam+Thmor+Pro&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <title>Fontes</title>
</head>
<body>
    <p>
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Minus soluta voluptatum amet odio nulla aperiam corporis, natus, dignissimos harum quibusdam cum perferendis necessitatibus, beatae sint saepe doloremque rerum tempore obcaecati.
    </p>
</body>
</html>

